beer.beer_description:
By Ogden Nash:

The truth I do not stretch or shove when I state that the dog is full of love. I've also found, by actual tess, a Moon Dog is the lovingest true story.

Also true is that this beer is made with Redskins, no fib or folly. Some 5800 of those jolly lollies.

Malt: American Ale, Pale, Munich, Toffee, Roast Barley, Caramunich.

Hops: Galaxy.

Yeast: British.

Other stuff: Heaps and heaps of redskins.

21°P & 30 IBU

items.checkin_comment: This old classic, and felt there was more of the raspberry candy aroma this time. Still not quite as rounded as my own efforts 😛, has that thin perfumy note that I’ve noticed in a few of their ”pastry” brews
